Author: Patrick Rothfuss
My Review:
Another positive rating to combat the crazy amount of negative comments.

I am happy to have had Kvothe's story in my life and will continue to follow until I can hopefully read the third and last book.

I get that you are frustrated and I do have to say that I am disappointed in Pat's intransparency but nothing he did had any real negative impact on anyone which is why I think this is way overblown.

Keep us posted Pat and keep doing what you enjoy!
